**Prescription**: Establish a regular void ritual on the Ritual Codex calendar. Once per month on a fixed dark-moon day, archive stale states and log completed cycles. Write date and contents in `void_codex.md`. Let the rhythm of release be as intentional as the rhythm of creation.

