**Prescription**: Schedule your attention audit on the Ritual Codex: run it every 7 days on the same day. Write results in `attention_codex.md`. Track how your attention patterns shift across cycles. The rhythmic audit reveals what the single audit cannot — the pulse beneath the pattern.

